  }, "Unsplash")), mdx("p", null, "One of the most important aspects of DeFi investing and yield farming is the risk assessment of the smart contract where the funds are being put. During 2020 there were multiple hacks, which exploited vulnerabilities in the DeFi protocols, leading to millions of dollars lost by the depositors. I've been involved in smart contract risk assessment since the DeFi craze started. Before that I was a CTO in the blockchain analytics company ", mdx("a", _extends({
